snippet.title: Ilysia | VR MMORPG | Team 21 Studio, LLC
snippet.description:
Ilysia has been funded on Kickstarter! Now is our chance to get as many stretch goals hit as we can! Head over to our campaign: 

https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/team21studio/ilysia-experience-the-glory-days-of-mmorpgs-again-in-vr

Please share this link everywhere you can to help spread awareness of Ilysia!

A MASSIVE thank you to our entire community for all your continued support, we wouldn't be here without you!

Ilysia Website: https://ilysiavr.com/

Team 21 Studio Website: https://team21studio.com/

Ilysia Discord: https://discord.com/invite/ilysia
